@startuml ntk10003-lookup-reservation-sequence

title NTK-10003: Unregistered Guest Self-Service Check-in\nReservation Lookup Orchestration Sequence

skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2
skinparam roundcorner 10
skinparam sequenceParticipant underline

actor "Guest" as Guest
participant "Kiosk UI" as Kiosk
participant "Kong API\nGateway" as Gateway
participant "svc-check-in\n(Orchestrator)" as CheckIn
participant "Redis" as Redis
participant "svc-reservations" as Reservations
participant "svc-partner-\nintegrations" as Partners
participant "svc-guest-\nprofiles" as Profiles
participant "svc-safety-\ncompliance" as Safety
participant "svc-gear-\ninventory" as Gear

== Identity Verification ==

Guest -> Kiosk : Select "Check in with\nConfirmation Code"
Kiosk -> Kiosk : Display 4-field verification form

Guest -> Kiosk : Enter last_name,\nconfirmation_code,\nadventure_date,\nparticipant_count

Kiosk -> Gateway : POST /check-ins/lookup-reservation\n{last_name, confirmation_code,\nadventure_date, participant_count,\nkiosk_device_id}

Gateway -> Gateway : Check gateway-level rate limit\n(5 per 15min per kiosk_device_id)

alt Rate Limit Exceeded at Gateway
    Gateway --> Kiosk : 429 Too Many Requests\n{retry_after_seconds}
    Kiosk -> Guest : "Too many attempts.\nPlease visit the service desk."
    note right : No artificial delay needed\nfor 429 responses
    return
end

Gateway -> CheckIn : Route request

== Step 1: Validate and Check App-Level Rate Limit ==

CheckIn -> Redis : Check app-level rate limit\nratelimit:lookup:{kiosk_device_id}
Redis --> CheckIn : {count, window_remaining}

alt Rate Limit Exceeded at App Level
    CheckIn --> Kiosk : 429 RATE_LIMIT_EXCEEDED
    return
end

CheckIn -> CheckIn : Normalize confirmation_code\nto uppercase, strip hyphens\nValidate adventure_date\nValidate participant_count 1-20

== Step 2: Reservation Lookup ==

CheckIn -> Reservations : POST /reservations/search\n{last_name, confirmation_code,\nadventure_date, participant_count}
note right : 2-second timeout\nNew composite index query

alt Reservation Found
    Reservations --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{reservation_id, adventure_name,\nparticipants[], booking_source}

else Reservation Not Found (404)
    Reservations --> CheckIn : 404 Not Found

    == Step 2a: Partner Fallback ==

    CheckIn -> CheckIn : Extract partner prefix\nfrom confirmation_code\n(EM-, TF-, WP-)

    alt Partner Identified
        CheckIn -> Partners : POST /partner-integrations/verify-booking\n{partner_id, confirmation_code, last_name}
        note right : 30-second timeout\nCircuit breaker: 50% error threshold

        alt Partner Confirms Booking
            Partners --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{booking_details}
            CheckIn -> Reservations : POST /reservations\n(create synced reservation)
            Reservations --> CheckIn : 201 Created\n{reservation_id}

        else Partner Booking Not Found
            Partners --> CheckIn : 404 Not Found
            CheckIn -> CheckIn : Apply 2-second\nartificial delay
            CheckIn -> Redis : Increment failure counter
            CheckIn --> Kiosk : 404 RESERVATION_NOT_FOUND\n"Visit service desk"
            Kiosk -> Guest : Display generic error\n"We couldn't find a\nmatching reservation."
            return

        else Circuit Breaker Open
            Partners --> CheckIn : 503 (circuit open)
            CheckIn -> CheckIn : Apply 2-second\nartificial delay
            CheckIn --> Kiosk : 404 RESERVATION_NOT_FOUND\n"Visit service desk\nwith priority queuing"
            Kiosk -> Guest : Display error + staff direction
            return
        end

    else No Partner Prefix / Unknown Partner
        CheckIn -> CheckIn : Apply 2-second\nartificial delay
        CheckIn -> Redis : Increment failure counter
        CheckIn --> Kiosk : 404 RESERVATION_NOT_FOUND
        Kiosk -> Guest : Display generic error
        return
    end
end

== Step 3: Guest Profile ==

CheckIn -> Profiles : GET /guest-profiles\n?reservation_id={id}

alt Profile Exists
    Profiles --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{guest_profile_id, profile_type}

else No Profile Found
    CheckIn -> Profiles : POST /guest-profiles/temporary\n{last_name, reservation_id}
    note right : 1-second timeout\nNew endpoint: minimal fields\nBypasses email/DOB requirements
    Profiles --> CheckIn : 201 Created\n{guest_profile_id,\nprofile_type: TEMPORARY}
end

== Step 4: Parallel Status Checks ==

par Safety Compliance Check (3s timeout)
    CheckIn -> Safety : GET /waivers\n?reservation_id={id}
    note right : Extended endpoint:\npreviously required guest_id only
    Safety --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{waiver_complete, waiver_url}

else Gear Assignment Check (3s timeout)
    CheckIn -> Gear : GET /gear-inventory/assignments\n?reservation_id={id}
    note right : Existing endpoint:\nalready supports reservation_id
    Gear --> CheckIn : 200 OK\n{gear_items[], pickup_location}
end

note over CheckIn : Graceful degradation:\nIf safety or gear call fails,\nproceed with null status fields.\nGuest completes manually.

== Step 5: Session Creation ==

CheckIn -> CheckIn : Generate JWT session token\n{guest_profile_id, reservation_id,\nkiosk_device_id, exp: +30min}
CheckIn -> Redis : Store session\nkey: session:{session_id}\nsecondary: kiosk:{device_id}\nTTL: 30 minutes

CheckIn --> Gateway : 200 OK
Gateway --> Kiosk : {session_token, reservation_id,\nguest_profile_id, adventure_name,\ncheck_in_status{waiver, gear},\nparticipants[]}

Kiosk -> Guest : Display check-in summary\nProceed with standard kiosk flow\n(waiver signing, gear confirmation,\nadventure briefing)

@enduml
